  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Open Hand sphere, base attack bonus +6.</p>\n<p>You may spend a move action to rapidly spin in place, generating heat and friction that cause the next unarmed strike you make before the start of your next turn to deal an additional amount of fire damage equal to your base attack bonus. While this talent is active, the hellish flames around your limbs cause your unarmed strikes to be treated as magical weapons when attacking incorporeal creatures; if your unarmed strikes would already be magical, such as because you are currently wearing an amulet of mighty fists, they instead deal full damage against incorporeal creatures. Creatures killed while this talent is active require those attempting to resurrect them to make a caster level check equal to 10 + your base attack bonus or fail. This is a supernatural effect.</p>\n",
